<ab facs="#facs_7_r2l24">Jr / den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> . nach rechts <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd geſtatten </ab>
